$ Oracle: Init parameter _OPTIMIZER_ANSWERING_QUERY_USING_STATS
@ _optimizer_answering_query_using_stats

As per MOS note 2896884.1, setting `_optimizer_answering_query_using_stats` enables or disables *hint usage reports*.
-
The description in `x$ksppi` is *enable statistics-based query transformation*.

